### 机场贵宾厅预约权益核验批量对账与审计服务 - API 测试示例
### 基础URL: http://localhost:8080/api/v1

### ========================================
### 健康检查
### ========================================

### 健康检查
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/health

### ========================================
### 会员权益 API
### ========================================

### 获取会员权益列表
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/member-benefits?page=1&per_page=10

### 获取会员权益列表 - 按状态筛选
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/member-benefits?status=active&page=1&per_page=10

### 获取会员权益列表 - 按会员等级筛选
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/member-benefits?member_level=platinum&page=1&per_page=10

### 获取单个会员权益
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/member-benefits/1

### 创建会员权益
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/member-benefits
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "member_name": "测试会员张三",
  "member_level": "gold",
  "remaining_quota": 8,
  "total_quota": 10,
  "valid_from": "2024-01-01",
  "valid_to": "2024-12-31",
  "responsible_person": "李运营",
  "batch_no": "BATCH-2024-TEST"
}

### 更新会员权益
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/member-benefits/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "remaining_quota": 7,
  "remarks": "使用了一次权益"
}

### 删除会员权益
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/member-benefits/11

### 检查权益过期
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/member-benefits/check-expiry
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### ========================================
### 预约记录 API
### ========================================

### 获取预约记录列表
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/reservations?page=1&per_page=10

### 获取预约记录列表 - 按状态筛选
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/reservations?status=confirmed&page=1&per_page=10

### 获取单个预约记录
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/reservations/1

### 创建预约记录
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/reservations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "member_benefit_id": 1,
  "member_name": "张明远",
  "flight_no": "CA1234",
  "flight_schedule_id": 1,
  "vip_lounge_name": "首都机场VIP厅A区",
  "reservation_time": "2024-06-20T10:00:00Z",
  "guest_count": 2,
  "responsible_person": "服务台小李",
  "batch_no": "RSV-BATCH-TEST"
}

### 更新预约记录
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/reservations/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "guest_count": 3,
  "remarks": "增加一位同行人"
}

### 删除预约记录
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/reservations/11

### 批量导入预检
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/reservations/batch-import/preview
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reservations": [
    {
      "member_benefit_id": 1,
      "member_name": "批量测试会员1",
      "flight_no": "CA1234",
      "flight_schedule_id": 1,
      "vip_lounge_name": "首都机场VIP厅A区",
      "reservation_time": "2024-06-20T10:00:00Z",
      "guest_count": 1,
      "responsible_person": "服务台小李"
    },
    {
      "member_benefit_id": 2,
      "member_name": "批量测试会员2",
      "flight_no": "MU5678",
      "flight_schedule_id": 2,
      "vip_lounge_name": "浦东机场VIP厅B区",
      "reservation_time": "2024-06-20T11:00:00Z",
      "guest_count": 2,
      "responsible_person": "服务台小王"
    }
  ],
  "batch_no": "BATCH-IMPORT-TEST-001"
}

### 执行批量导入
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/reservations/batch-import
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reservations": [
    {
      "member_benefit_id": 1,
      "member_name": "批量导入会员1",
      "flight_no": "CA1234",
      "flight_schedule_id": 1,
      "vip_lounge_name": "首都机场VIP厅A区",
      "reservation_time": "2024-06-20T10:00:00Z",
      "guest_count": 1,
      "responsible_person": "服务台小李"
    }
  ],
  "batch_no": "BATCH-IMPORT-EXEC-001"
}

### 状态流转 - 提交审核
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/reservations/1/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action": "submit",
  "operator": "服务台小李",
  "remarks": "提交审核"
}

### 状态流转 - 审核通过
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/reservations/1/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action": "approve",
  "operator": "审核员甲",
  "remarks": "审核通过"
}

### 状态流转 - 驳回（必须填写原因）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/reservations/1/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action": "reject",
  "operator": "审核员乙",
  "reason": "同行人数量超限",
  "remarks": "请减少同行人数量"
}

### 获取允许的状态流转
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/reservations/1/transitions

### ========================================
### 航班时段 API
### ========================================

### 获取航班时段列表
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/flight-schedules?page=1&per_page=10

### 获取单个航班时段
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/flight-schedules/1

### 创建航班时段
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/flight-schedules
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "flight_no": "CA9999",
  "departure_airport": "北京首都T3",
  "arrival_airport": "深圳宝安T3",
  "scheduled_depart": "2024-06-20T08:00:00Z",
  "scheduled_arrive": "2024-06-20T11:00:00Z",
  "flight_status": "scheduled",
  "vip_lounge_capacity": 50,
  "responsible_person": "调度员张三",
  "batch_no": "FLT-BATCH-TEST"
}

### 更新航班时段
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/flight-schedules/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "flight_status": "boarding",
  "remarks": "开始登机"
}

### 归档航班时段
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/flight-schedules/1/archive
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 批量归档航班时段
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/flight-schedules/batch-archive
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "flight_schedule_ids": [1, 2, 3],
  "operator": "调度员李四"
}

### ========================================
### 候补名单 API
### ========================================

### 获取候补名单列表
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/waitlist?page=1&per_page=10

### 获取候补名单 - 按航班筛选
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/waitlist?flight_schedule_id=1&page=1&per_page=10

### 获取单个候补记录
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/waitlist/1

### 创建候补记录
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/waitlist
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "member_benefit_id": 1,
  "flight_schedule_id": 1,
  "member_name": "候补测试会员",
  "member_level": "gold",
  "responsible_person": "调度员张三",
  "batch_no": "WTL-BATCH-TEST"
}

### 计算入场优先级
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/waitlist/calculate-priority
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "member_level": "platinum",
  "remaining_quota": 15,
  "waiting_minutes": 45
}

### 安排候补入场
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/waitlist/arrange
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "flight_schedule_id": 1,
  "available_seats": 2,
  "operator": "调度员李四"
}

### ========================================
### 核验结果 API
### ========================================

### 获取核验结果列表
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/verifications?page=1&per_page=10

### 获取单个核验结果
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/verifications/1

### 创建核验结果
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/verifications
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reservation_id": 1,
  "member_benefit_id": 1,
  "flight_schedule_id": 1,
  "verification_type": "reservation",
  "result": "passed",
  "verified_quota": 2,
  "verified_companions": 1,
  "responsible_person": "核验员甲",
  "batch_no": "VER-BATCH-TEST"
}

### 核验权益资格
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/verifications/verify-eligibility
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "member_benefit_id": 1,
  "flight_schedule_id": 1,
  "guest_count": 2,
  "operator": "核验员甲"
}

### ========================================
### 异常事件 API
### ========================================

### 获取异常事件列表
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/exceptions?page=1&per_page=10

### 获取异常事件 - 按状态筛选
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/exceptions?status=open&page=1&per_page=10

### 获取单个异常事件
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/exceptions/1

### 创建异常事件
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/exceptions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "event_type": "quota_exceeded",
  "entity_type": "member_benefit",
  "entity_id": 1,
  "trigger_field": "remaining_quota",
  "threshold_value": "1",
  "actual_value": "0",
  "severity": "medium",
  "responsible_person": "李运营",
  "batch_no": "EVT-BATCH-TEST"
}

### 处理异常事件
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/exceptions/handle
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "event_id": 1,
  "handler": "李运营",
  "handling_result": "已补充配额",
  "remarks": "紧急处理完成"
}

### 获取待处理异常事件
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/exceptions/open

### ========================================
### 审计日志 API
### ========================================

### 获取审计日志列表
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/audit-logs?page=1&per_page=10

### 获取审计日志 - 按实体类型筛选
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/audit-logs?entity_type=reservation&page=1&per_page=10

### 获取单个审计日志
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/audit-logs/1

### 获取实体相关的审计日志
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/audit-logs/entity/reservation/1

### ========================================
### 统计 API
### ========================================

### 获取核验通过率统计
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/statistics/verification?start_date=2024-01-01&end_date=2024-12-31

### 获取候补转入率统计
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/statistics/waitlist?start_date=2024-01-01&end_date=2024-12-31

### 获取入场使用率统计
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/statistics/usage?start_date=2024-01-01&end_date=2024-12-31

### 获取统计 - 按批次筛选
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/statistics/verification?batch_no=BATCH-2024-001

### 获取统计 - 按角色筛选
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/statistics/verification?role=核验员甲
